WEBVTT

1
00:00:15.950 --> 00:00:17.890
(Lee Jun Young)

2
00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:25.660
(Lee Ju Myoung)

3
00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:34.340
(Jeon Hye Jin. Jin Goo)

4
00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:51.920
(Reborn Rookie)

5
00:00:55.383 --> 00:00:56.483
(Midanon)

6
00:01:22.873 --> 00:01:25.243
Code Blue in Neurosurgery.

7
00:01:25.613 --> 00:01:30.183
All Neurosurgery staff
report to the VIP Ward ICU.

8
00:01:30.523 --> 00:01:32.923
Code Blue in Neurosurgery.

9
00:01:33.123 --> 00:01:37.693
All Neurosurgery staff
report to the VIP Ward ICU.

10
00:01:53.343 --> 00:01:54.473
Defibrillator. now.

11
00:01:57.513 --> 00:01:58.683
Charge to 200.

12
00:01:59.683 --> 00:02:00.683
Clear.

13
00:02:02.283 --> 00:02:03.323
Another 200.

14
00:02:15.163 --> 00:02:17.503
He's still alive.

15
00:02:18.663 --> 00:02:19.873
Get the ECMO ready. now.

16
00:02:20.233 --> 00:02:22.533
Call the transport team and contact CS.

17
00:02:23.303 --> 00:02:25.093
- Everybody. move.
- Yes. sir.

18
00:02:25.173 --> 00:02:27.173
- Right now!
- Yes. sir.

19
00:02:30.613 --> 00:02:32.663
Why are you giving up already? Do more!

20
00:02:32.743 --> 00:02:34.283
You have to do everything you can.

21
00:02:35.713 --> 00:02:38.823
Do not disrespect the deceased.
You are not a family member.

22
00:02:43.693 --> 00:02:44.723
Mom!

23
00:02:45.623 --> 00:02:47.063
Mom. are you okay?

24
00:02:55.303 --> 00:02:56.303
(Jae Gyeong)

25
00:02:58.243 --> 00:02:59.943
(Seok Do)

26
00:03:02.273 --> 00:03:03.703
The person you have
called is unavailable...

27
00:03:03.783 --> 00:03:05.283
Kang Jae Gyeong. I swear I'll...

28
00:03:07.753 --> 00:03:09.553
(Authorized Personnel Only)

29
00:03:13.023 --> 00:03:14.023
Professor.

30
00:03:15.153 --> 00:03:18.163
I'd like to be alone for a bit.

31
00:03:35.513 --> 00:03:36.613
What are you doing?

32
00:03:37.713 --> 00:03:38.713
Jae Seong.

33
00:03:38.913 --> 00:03:40.733
Did Kang Jae Gyeong tell you
to finish off our father for good?

34
00:03:40.813 --> 00:03:43.123
What did you two do to our father?

35
00:03:44.583 --> 00:03:46.353
I think she gave him sleeping pills.

36
00:03:46.793 --> 00:03:49.153
If we don't counteract it now. he'll die.

37
00:03:49.323 --> 00:03:50.363
What are you talking about?

38
00:03:51.093 --> 00:03:52.593
Are you saying we can save him?

39
00:03:53.023 --> 00:03:54.763
His heartbeat has returned. faintly.

40
00:03:56.663 --> 00:03:59.003
We have to save him. no matter what.

41
00:04:03.543 --> 00:04:04.843
Are you sure about this?

42
00:04:05.103 --> 00:04:06.973
If you're messing with
me about my father...

43
00:04:13.553 --> 00:04:14.553
Father.

44
00:04:15.883 --> 00:04:17.883
- Father.
- Father.

45
00:04:25.063 --> 00:04:26.063
He's breathing.

46
00:04:26.993 --> 00:04:28.263
Father is breathing.

47
00:04:31.203 --> 00:04:32.333
I've got a pulse.

48
00:04:32.963 --> 00:04:35.003
- He's stable.
- Father.

49
00:04:35.873 --> 00:04:38.273
It's me. Jae Seong is here.

50
00:04:39.673 --> 00:04:43.483
Right. He couldn't die unjustly like this.

51
00:04:44.483 --> 00:04:45.703
My father won't be the one...

52
00:04:45.783 --> 00:04:47.153
who dies at the hands
of that witch Jae Gyeong.

53
00:04:49.983 --> 00:04:51.183
(Jae Gyeong)

54
00:04:54.653 --> 00:04:56.123
(Jae Gyeong)

55
00:04:58.863 --> 00:05:00.993
You go and keep your wife happy.

56
00:05:03.093 --> 00:05:04.083
Tell her our father is dead.

57
00:05:04.163 --> 00:05:05.763
Make sure she believes
it. And say nothing else.

58
00:05:06.003 --> 00:05:08.423
He was pronounced dead a moment ago.

59
00:05:08.503 --> 00:05:09.843
What will you do?

60
00:05:14.313 --> 00:05:15.343
This time.

61
00:05:16.473 --> 00:05:18.513
I have to finally do my
duty as the eldest son.

62
00:05:21.853 --> 00:05:25.853
(Unclaimed Body)

63
00:05:36.633 --> 00:05:40.203
Dad. aren't you sad? Grandpa passed away.

64
00:05:42.533 --> 00:05:43.573
Congratulations. honey.

65
00:05:43.873 --> 00:05:45.543
Everything turned out
just the way you wanted.

66
00:05:46.673 --> 00:05:49.743
I just want to know
the truth of how he died.

67
00:05:51.343 --> 00:05:52.443
I guess I'll get what's coming to me.

68
00:05:54.383 --> 00:05:56.173
I should be the one glaring here.

69
00:05:56.253 --> 00:05:58.623
Being associated with you has
brought me nothing but bad luck.

70
00:06:00.793 --> 00:06:02.293
I swore before our father.

71
00:06:02.593 --> 00:06:05.093
From now on. you. Kang
Bang Geul. are my only sister.

72
00:06:05.423 --> 00:06:06.344
Father.

73
00:06:06.424 --> 00:06:08.963
And that I'll finally start
acting like a proper big brother.

74
00:06:13.133 --> 00:06:14.133
Father.

75
00:06:17.743 --> 00:06:18.773
Father.

76
00:06:19.143 --> 00:06:21.843
Hang on a little longer.
Okay? We're almost there.

77
00:06:29.553 --> 00:06:32.423
Why is it doing this again? But he's dead.

78
00:06:44.603 --> 00:06:45.603
Bang Geul!

79
00:06:47.073 --> 00:06:48.103
Bang Geul!

80
00:06:55.213 --> 00:06:58.083
Hey! Someone's hurt
here. Call an ambulance.

81
00:06:58.983 --> 00:07:00.083
Ambulance!

82
00:07:01.083 --> 00:07:02.913
Stop running. I'm so sleepy.

83
00:07:04.953 --> 00:07:05.953
Bang Geul.

84
00:07:06.953 --> 00:07:09.153
Why are you making so much noise?

85
00:07:10.393 --> 00:07:12.493
You're giving me a splitting headache.

86
00:07:14.993 --> 00:07:16.033
Bang Geul...

87
00:07:25.603 --> 00:07:27.043
(Paramedics)

88
00:07:43.253 --> 00:07:44.963
{\an8}Sir. you're here.

89
00:07:45.323 --> 00:07:46.463
{\an8}Is everyone okay?

90
00:07:48.033 --> 00:07:49.063
Oh my.

91
00:07:50.603 --> 00:07:53.373
What happened to your head?
Shouldn't you go to the hospital?

92
00:07:53.673 --> 00:07:55.873
They said it's just a small cut. I'm okay.

93
00:07:56.203 --> 00:07:58.503
For a second. I thought
it was really serious.

94
00:07:59.243 --> 00:08:00.513
Right. Hwang?

95
00:08:03.383 --> 00:08:07.073
What? You were so worried
Young Lady might die.

96
00:08:07.153 --> 00:08:09.003
You were the one who swept
her up and ran like crazy.

97
00:08:09.083 --> 00:08:11.623
so why are you just standing
there looking lost now?

98
00:08:11.853 --> 00:08:12.883
Go to the emergency room.

99
00:08:13.183 --> 00:08:16.023
Get a CT and an MRI so you
don't complain about the pain later.

100
00:08:16.193 --> 00:08:19.393
Don't be so dramatic. You're
holding up a busy woman.

101
00:08:20.063 --> 00:08:21.063
Thank you.

102
00:08:21.993 --> 00:08:23.663
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

103
00:08:25.433 --> 00:08:28.423
Hey. how could you let
Secretary Jo take that?

104
00:08:28.503 --> 00:08:30.003
Do you really want Choiseong to fail?

105
00:08:31.003 --> 00:08:32.273
My point exactly.

106
00:08:33.813 --> 00:08:37.703
Just be straight with us.
What on earth are you thinking?

107
00:08:37.783 --> 00:08:38.783
Please.

108
00:08:39.083 --> 00:08:40.283
I need a word with you.

109
00:08:40.513 --> 00:08:43.013
- With you. sir?
- I must discuss something urgent.

110
00:08:43.113 --> 00:08:45.583
But I think I need to hear
what he has to say first.

111
00:08:46.123 --> 00:08:47.653
I feel like I really need to know.

112
00:08:57.563 --> 00:08:58.563
Hey. Hwang Jun Hyeon.

113
00:09:01.603 --> 00:09:03.023
Should I go tell Kang Jae Gyeong...

114
00:09:03.103 --> 00:09:05.073
you're teaming up with
Taeha to backstab her?

115
00:09:06.973 --> 00:09:07.973
Or...

116
00:09:10.313 --> 00:09:11.743
should I take this to Chairman Na?

117
00:09:12.183 --> 00:09:13.413
Where did you get that?

118
00:09:15.183 --> 00:09:17.223
I stole it. From Chairman Na's house.

119
00:09:17.653 --> 00:09:19.943
You have no idea how
dangerous Na Byeong Mo is.

120
00:09:20.023 --> 00:09:21.993
What will you do if something
happens because of this?

121
00:09:23.323 --> 00:09:26.623
Open your eyes. Wake
up. Can't you hear your dad?

122
00:09:29.263 --> 00:09:30.533
Why are you treating me like this?

123
00:09:31.533 --> 00:09:33.973
- What?
- You're worried about me.

124
00:09:34.433 --> 00:09:36.233
This whole time. you put
on an act to protect me.

125
00:09:39.143 --> 00:09:42.163
This is about my sister and my dad.
If anyone gets revenge. it'll be me.

126
00:09:42.243 --> 00:09:43.983
Why are you getting involved when
you have nothing to do with this?

127
00:09:44.183 --> 00:09:45.313
Why are you telling me to back off?

128
00:09:45.843 --> 00:09:49.503
- What gives you the right?
- Fine. I'm afraid you'll get hurt.

129
00:09:49.583 --> 00:09:52.023
and that your mother will be put
in danger. I can't sleep at night.

130
00:09:52.583 --> 00:09:54.713
I'm going crazy worrying
that you'll get hurt by them...

131
00:09:54.793 --> 00:09:56.623
while seeking revenge for your dad.

132
00:09:58.923 --> 00:09:59.963
"Them"?

133
00:10:02.093 --> 00:10:04.733
Is Chairman Na also
involved in my father's death?

134
00:10:05.603 --> 00:10:07.403
Don't tell me he's an
accomplice of Kang Jae Gyeong's.

135
00:10:08.633 --> 00:10:09.633
Hwang Jun Hyeon!

136
00:10:13.273 --> 00:10:15.363
I'm running forensics on
the security guard's phone...

137
00:10:15.443 --> 00:10:16.843
to find the hospital CCTV footage.

138
00:10:19.183 --> 00:10:20.883
Out of greed to take over Choiseong.

139
00:10:21.813 --> 00:10:23.783
she framed Kang Jae Gyeong for it.

140
00:10:25.553 --> 00:10:27.093
It was Na Eun Se who killed him.

141
00:10:34.663 --> 00:10:35.663
Are you sure?

142
00:10:44.073 --> 00:10:45.073
My dad...

143
00:10:46.573 --> 00:10:51.083
was just used by everyone before he died?

144
00:10:58.983 --> 00:11:00.723
I'm so grateful for all your help.

145
00:11:02.193 --> 00:11:03.293
but you need to stay out of this now.

146
00:11:04.693 --> 00:11:05.693
This is my fight.

147
00:11:07.133 --> 00:11:10.093
How do you plan to take
on murderers all by yourself?

148
00:11:11.163 --> 00:11:12.633
It's because I feel so sorry for him.

149
00:11:14.073 --> 00:11:15.973
That there were people
who cared for my dad.

150
00:11:16.903 --> 00:11:18.073
That his life...

151
00:11:18.873 --> 00:11:21.013
wasn't a lonely departure at all.

152
00:11:21.613 --> 00:11:22.713
That's what I want to show.

153
00:11:37.723 --> 00:11:38.723
But...

154
00:11:41.533 --> 00:11:42.863
don't become a bad person.

155
00:11:44.203 --> 00:11:45.203
Kang Bang Geul.

156
00:11:49.333 --> 00:11:52.003
Getting blood on your hands. being cruel...

157
00:11:52.773 --> 00:11:54.043
This thing called revenge...

158
00:11:56.543 --> 00:11:58.113
It will destroy you too.

159
00:12:00.483 --> 00:12:02.113
Don't let that happen to you.

160
00:12:03.113 --> 00:12:04.453
I'll do the dirty work.

161
00:12:08.993 --> 00:12:10.493
I told you. this is my revenge.

162
00:12:11.663 --> 00:12:14.293
- Why would you...
- Your father wouldn't want it.

163
00:12:18.303 --> 00:12:20.023
No father in the world
would want his daughter...

164
00:12:20.103 --> 00:12:21.373
to be ruined because of him.

165
00:12:24.903 --> 00:12:26.143
Not a single one.

166
00:12:39.823 --> 00:12:40.953
Be honest with me.

167
00:12:42.053 --> 00:12:43.793
Do you have a secret daughter
stashed away somewhere?

168
00:12:44.693 --> 00:12:45.723
Goodness.

169
00:12:47.833 --> 00:12:49.993
I'm letting you in on my revenge.

170
00:12:52.633 --> 00:12:54.273
So do everything with me.

171
00:12:56.203 --> 00:12:57.203
All right.

172
00:13:00.673 --> 00:13:03.543
(Chairman Na Byeong Mo)

173
00:13:03.913 --> 00:13:06.483
First off. let's take down
that jerk. Secretary Jo.

174
00:13:19.963 --> 00:13:21.193
About today...

175
00:13:22.333 --> 00:13:24.503
I believe you owe me an explanation.

176
00:13:31.243 --> 00:13:33.403
Before that. you should
get a new secretary.

177
00:13:33.743 --> 00:13:36.343
How long are you going to
keep a thug by your side?

178
00:13:36.943 --> 00:13:39.043
Especially now that you're the
head of a major conglomerate.

179
00:13:40.713 --> 00:13:42.103
I mean. sure. he made
me look like an idiot...

180
00:13:42.183 --> 00:13:43.883
who couldn't even handle Kang Bang Geul.

181
00:13:44.223 --> 00:13:45.223
But...

182
00:13:46.853 --> 00:13:48.143
because that jerk wanted all the credit.

183
00:13:48.223 --> 00:13:49.853
our grand plan was almost ruined.

184
00:13:49.993 --> 00:13:52.963
There are plenty of smart guys
out there. Why use a punk like him?

185
00:13:53.863 --> 00:13:55.993
- Hwang Jun Hyeon.
- That's enough.

186
00:13:58.703 --> 00:14:01.633
Hand it over to Taeha Energy
and tell them to do a tech review.

187
00:14:01.873 --> 00:14:03.873
We'll see when the results come in.

188
00:14:04.143 --> 00:14:07.443
Whether I need brains or brawn.

189
00:14:16.783 --> 00:14:20.053
Won't Kang Jae Gyeong be suspicious?
There was an accident. after all.

190
00:14:20.283 --> 00:14:23.653
She knows her brother is acting
out. so she'll assume it was him.

191
00:14:25.263 --> 00:14:26.923
Jae Seong is not a bad
person to use as a shield.

192
00:14:27.193 --> 00:14:30.193
A chairman who had the
technology for the sale stolen?

193
00:14:30.703 --> 00:14:33.203
Kang Jae Gyeong's position
is going to be pretty shaky.

194
00:14:39.003 --> 00:14:40.093
(Lee Sang Jae)

195
00:14:40.173 --> 00:14:41.273
Forensics complete.

196
00:14:41.613 --> 00:14:43.783
I've found the original
hospital CCTV footage.

197
00:14:46.983 --> 00:14:48.683
It's going to be quite a show.

198
00:14:50.923 --> 00:14:52.283
You can look forward to it. Chairman Na.

199
00:15:08.733 --> 00:15:10.973
What is she doing in front of
someone else's house at this hour?

200
00:15:14.413 --> 00:15:15.943
Out of greed to take over Choiseong.

201
00:15:16.313 --> 00:15:18.343
she framed Kang Jae Gyeong for it.

202
00:15:19.113 --> 00:15:20.683
It was Na Eun Se who killed him.

203
00:15:33.693 --> 00:15:36.433
Has she lost her mind? So
she wants to go at it. is that it?

204
00:15:45.743 --> 00:15:46.773
Are you okay?

205
00:15:47.073 --> 00:15:49.443
- Are you crazy?
- She's the one who's crazy.

206
00:15:49.673 --> 00:15:50.713
Hey!

207
00:15:52.213 --> 00:15:55.083
What are you staring at?
Upset that you didn't die?

208
00:15:55.713 --> 00:15:57.353
Then go to Kang Jae Gyeong.

209
00:15:57.983 --> 00:15:59.653
Why are you bothering an
innocent person to kill you?

210
00:16:00.523 --> 00:16:01.723
Are you not afraid of anything anymore?

211
00:16:04.393 --> 00:16:05.763
Think you own the world now?

212
00:16:06.093 --> 00:16:07.093
Bang Geul.

213
00:16:10.163 --> 00:16:11.633
I'm your sister-in-law.

214
00:16:12.363 --> 00:16:14.203
There's a line you shouldn't cross.

215
00:16:16.903 --> 00:16:19.543
I'll show you exactly what
it means to cross the line.

216
00:16:20.173 --> 00:16:21.773
- You just wait.
- Sure.

217
00:16:23.073 --> 00:16:24.083
Go ahead.

218
00:16:25.413 --> 00:16:27.553
Why should I be scared of someone like you?

219
00:16:30.653 --> 00:16:31.753
That's enough. Go inside.

220
00:16:32.053 --> 00:16:34.053
- Get inside.
- Let go.

221
00:16:34.693 --> 00:16:36.393
Taking her side just because she's family.

222
00:16:37.193 --> 00:16:38.193
I swear...

223
00:16:38.993 --> 00:16:41.933
I'm so sick and tired
of this Kang household.

224
00:16:57.783 --> 00:17:01.413
She's becoming the spitting
image of her father. isn't she?

225
00:17:03.213 --> 00:17:05.053
Hey. did that startle you?

226
00:17:05.853 --> 00:17:07.793
Hey. I heard you hurt your
head. Is it because it hurts?

227
00:17:08.123 --> 00:17:10.293
- Let's go to the hospital.
- Jae Seong.

228
00:17:18.603 --> 00:17:19.703
Na Eun Se...

229
00:17:21.333 --> 00:17:22.973
Those jerks at Taeha...

230
00:17:47.993 --> 00:17:49.393
Don't trust that girl.

231
00:17:50.163 --> 00:17:55.553
Think Chairman Na. who never
loses. would give her to you for nothing?

232
00:17:55.633 --> 00:17:56.833
Come on.

233
00:17:57.473 --> 00:17:59.943
Trust me. you don't have
to worry about Eun Se.

234
00:18:03.713 --> 00:18:04.913
You darn fool.

235
00:18:06.643 --> 00:18:08.013
You idiot.

236
00:18:12.023 --> 00:18:13.353
It's my fault.

237
00:18:17.123 --> 00:18:20.593
If it weren't for you. this
wouldn't have happened to Father.

238
00:18:23.133 --> 00:18:24.863
It's your fault.

239
00:18:44.053 --> 00:18:48.193
- Mom!
- Let go! I'm going to get him.

240
00:18:48.423 --> 00:18:50.623
Mom. first. just calm down.

241
00:18:50.863 --> 00:18:53.363
Jae Seong must be
completely torn apart inside.

242
00:18:54.793 --> 00:18:55.893
And I Jun...

243
00:18:56.663 --> 00:18:58.533
How can we raise him
with a mother like that?

244
00:18:59.163 --> 00:19:01.703
Are they even human? How could they...

245
00:19:01.803 --> 00:19:04.903
How could they do that to your father? How?

246
00:19:05.143 --> 00:19:06.173
I know. Mom.

247
00:19:06.873 --> 00:19:09.173
I want to kill them right now too.

248
00:19:11.083 --> 00:19:12.283
I'm holding back for Dad's sake.

249
00:19:13.113 --> 00:19:16.353
I'll make those lowlifes turn
on each other and draw blood.

250
00:19:16.453 --> 00:19:17.723
We will absolutely not be broken.

251
00:19:19.653 --> 00:19:20.653
Mom.

252
00:19:21.723 --> 00:19:22.823
How...

253
00:19:23.923 --> 00:19:25.023
How...

254
00:19:26.463 --> 00:19:27.593
Calm down.

255
00:19:31.933 --> 00:19:33.563
We're all ready. Chairman.

256
00:19:37.773 --> 00:19:39.423
I told you to wait until you take over...

257
00:19:39.503 --> 00:19:40.913
as president of C&T.

258
00:19:41.313 --> 00:19:43.643
I have to file for divorce
anyway for I Jun's sake.

259
00:19:44.483 --> 00:19:45.643
Since I'm getting a divorce anyway.

260
00:19:46.013 --> 00:19:47.853
I don't want to stay in that
house a single day longer.

261
00:19:48.283 --> 00:19:49.953
This doesn't look good.

262
00:19:50.283 --> 00:19:51.753
What does that matter?

263
00:19:52.723 --> 00:19:54.493
Kang Jae Gyeong is in the palm of our hand.

264
00:19:59.293 --> 00:20:00.563
(Choiseong C&T Managing
Director Kwon Beom Sik)

265
00:20:01.363 --> 00:20:02.433
Yes. Managing Director Kwon.

266
00:20:06.863 --> 00:20:08.233
What are you talking about?

267
00:20:11.303 --> 00:20:12.843
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

268
00:20:15.143 --> 00:20:16.213
Dismissing the Executive Director?

269
00:20:17.513 --> 00:20:18.503
Says who?

270
00:20:18.583 --> 00:20:20.953
Personnel decisions are
the chairman's prerogative.

271
00:20:22.253 --> 00:20:23.413
If you kick me out.

272
00:20:23.983 --> 00:20:25.353
do you think your position will be safe?

273
00:20:26.583 --> 00:20:27.723
I'm scared.

274
00:20:28.993 --> 00:20:31.793
Am I really getting kicked
out by the likes of Na Eun Se?

275
00:20:37.233 --> 00:20:38.333
You'll regret this.

276
00:20:50.613 --> 00:20:52.183
Don't you think you pushed her too hard?

277
00:20:52.543 --> 00:20:54.383
You have to provoke them to
get them to show their hand.

278
00:20:55.253 --> 00:20:58.083
- I took a leap. trusting you.
- Gosh.

279
00:20:59.923 --> 00:21:01.553
You said you found the
hospital's CCTV footage?

280
00:21:01.923 --> 00:21:03.943
I searched the house of
the security guard who died.

281
00:21:04.023 --> 00:21:05.463
and I found his cellphone.

282
00:21:09.293 --> 00:21:10.903
This is the footage from
the forensic analysis.

283
00:21:16.403 --> 00:21:19.103
How far will Na Eun Se run wild?

284
00:21:20.173 --> 00:21:21.843
Are you just going to stand by
and watch Kang Jae Gyeong?

285
00:21:22.573 --> 00:21:25.783
Leak the CCTV transcripts and
let's destroy Choiseong. Father.

286
00:21:25.943 --> 00:21:28.113
Don't act rashly. Just wait.

287
00:21:28.853 --> 00:21:30.553
Until when?

288
00:21:31.553 --> 00:21:32.553
Darn it.

289
00:21:37.763 --> 00:21:40.393
(Jeong Hak Hui. President of Hayoung Daily)

290
00:21:45.033 --> 00:21:46.033
President Jeong.

291
00:21:46.833 --> 00:21:47.933
That tip from back then...

292
00:21:48.433 --> 00:21:49.503
Let's release it.

293
00:21:49.703 --> 00:21:50.793
("Choiseong Family and
Chairman Kang Yong Ho's Death")

294
00:21:50.873 --> 00:21:51.873
("The Hospital Room Mystery")

295
00:21:51.973 --> 00:21:52.963
("Kang Yong Ho's Death Rumors...")

296
00:21:53.043 --> 00:21:54.043
("Hospital CCTV. Transcripts Out")

297
00:21:54.573 --> 00:21:55.593
{\an8}At first.

298
00:21:55.673 --> 00:21:57.603
{\an8}she was going to drug
Father with the sleeping pills...

299
00:21:57.683 --> 00:22:00.243
{\an8}she got from Professor Min
so Father wouldn't wake up.

300
00:22:00.583 --> 00:22:02.413
{\an8}But then Father's eyes suddenly shot open.

301
00:22:02.853 --> 00:22:03.903
{\an8}so she just grabbed the pillow...

302
00:22:03.983 --> 00:22:05.983
{\an8}and just... She smothered him.

303
00:22:06.083 --> 00:22:07.923
{\an8}Your husband is my accomplice.

304
00:22:08.323 --> 00:22:10.523
{\an8}You want to see whose crime is worse?

305
00:22:10.823 --> 00:22:11.913
(If this is true. boycott Choiseong.)

306
00:22:11.993 --> 00:22:12.913
(Life sentence is too good for them.)

307
00:22:12.993 --> 00:22:13.913
(Are they mad for the chairmanship?)

308
00:22:13.993 --> 00:22:14.993
(What do you think about this article?)

309
00:22:15.233 --> 00:22:16.333
(The new recording is the key evidence.)

310
00:22:16.633 --> 00:22:19.223
{\an8}("The Suspicious Death of
Former Chairman Kang Yong Ho")

311
00:22:19.303 --> 00:22:22.533
{\an8}("Who Was the Last Visitor?")

312
00:22:23.803 --> 00:22:26.503
I told her to wait. Did she
have to go and cause trouble?

313
00:22:29.173 --> 00:22:30.233
("The Suspicious Death of
Former Chairman Kang Yong Ho")

314
00:22:30.313 --> 00:22:31.543
("Who Was the Last Visitor?")

315
00:22:33.313 --> 00:22:35.573
Chairman Na. There seems to be a problem...

316
00:22:35.653 --> 00:22:37.483
with the hydrogen
technology file from Choiseong.

317
00:22:37.983 --> 00:22:39.273
We checked it several times.

318
00:22:39.353 --> 00:22:42.093
and it's an older version than
what Taeha Energy already has.

319
00:22:46.363 --> 00:22:48.133
It's going to be quite a show.

320
00:22:49.293 --> 00:22:50.663
You can look forward to it. Chairman Na.

321
00:22:51.503 --> 00:22:53.563
Hwang Jun Hyeon. that jerk.

322
00:23:00.673 --> 00:23:03.043
(Choiseong Group Emergency Press Conference)

323
00:23:06.313 --> 00:23:10.313
For the shock and disappointment
many of you must be feeling.

324
00:23:10.753 --> 00:23:13.283
I offer my deepest apologies.

325
00:23:15.753 --> 00:23:17.663
After long deliberation.

326
00:23:18.223 --> 00:23:20.823
I came to the conclusion
that I could no longer hide this.

327
00:23:22.933 --> 00:23:24.433
That is why I am standing here today.

328
00:23:26.563 --> 00:23:27.563
The truth is.

329
00:23:28.503 --> 00:23:30.433
in regard to my father's death.

330
00:23:33.773 --> 00:23:36.713
- I am being blackmailed.
- Blackmailed?

331
00:23:38.613 --> 00:23:40.543
Is it true that you visited
his hospital room that day?

332
00:23:40.883 --> 00:23:42.713
Are you denying the
contents of the recording?

333
00:23:42.983 --> 00:23:44.623
The person who used the
fabricated recording and video...

334
00:23:44.723 --> 00:23:48.353
from the article. to demand
money from my late father.

335
00:23:48.823 --> 00:23:49.853
and the person who recently broke into...

336
00:23:50.193 --> 00:23:52.993
the Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

337
00:23:53.563 --> 00:23:56.693
and leaked our core hydrogen technology.

338
00:23:58.063 --> 00:24:02.273
- are. I presume. one and the same.
- Have you identified the suspect?

339
00:24:02.433 --> 00:24:03.903
Using the CCTV footage as evidence.

340
00:24:04.233 --> 00:24:06.003
we have turned over
their identity to the police.

341
00:24:06.503 --> 00:24:08.573
I also believe the real
culprit who killed my father.

342
00:24:09.113 --> 00:24:11.013
is part of the same group.

343
00:24:11.113 --> 00:24:13.983
Are you saying that the late Chairman
Kang Yong Ho was murdered?

344
00:24:17.723 --> 00:24:20.053
We've secured circumstantial
evidence about the real culprit.

345
00:24:27.963 --> 00:24:28.963
(Choiseong Group
Emergency Press Conference)

346
00:24:29.993 --> 00:24:31.003
- What?
- What on earth?

347
00:24:31.863 --> 00:24:33.203
Isn't that Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong?

348
00:24:43.743 --> 00:24:48.383
Are you saying the culprit murdered
your father and framed you for it?

349
00:24:48.613 --> 00:24:49.673
Do you have the original copy as well?

350
00:24:49.753 --> 00:24:53.143
You said "group." Does that
mean it wasn't a lone perpetrator?

351
00:24:53.223 --> 00:24:55.843
Please reveal their identity. Are
they an employee at Choiseong?

352
00:24:55.923 --> 00:24:59.063
- Why show the CCTV footage now?
- No longer...

353
00:25:03.463 --> 00:25:05.203
will I allow my father's death...

354
00:25:06.903 --> 00:25:08.303
to be exploited.

355
00:25:09.573 --> 00:25:11.103
So that the deceased may rest in peace.

356
00:25:13.073 --> 00:25:14.273
I beg this of you.

357
00:25:18.243 --> 00:25:21.153
(Choiseong Group
Emergency Press Conference)

358
00:25:24.153 --> 00:25:26.183
Her acting is giving me chills.

359
00:25:30.523 --> 00:25:33.363
(Choiseong Group
Emergency Press Conference)

360
00:25:33.723 --> 00:25:37.903
Kang Jae Gyeong is using
my dad until the very end.

361
00:25:50.373 --> 00:25:51.743
Public opinion has completely shifted.

362
00:25:52.083 --> 00:25:53.713
Speculation about the real
culprit is also running rampant.

363
00:25:54.383 --> 00:25:57.603
Since Director Na is also
implicated in the recording.

364
00:25:57.683 --> 00:26:00.223
if this goes wrong. the
focus could shift to Taeha.

365
00:26:02.493 --> 00:26:04.383
What should I do. Father?

366
00:26:04.463 --> 00:26:07.723
A blade swung recklessly
will cut you as well.

367
00:26:10.363 --> 00:26:12.663
Why does Kang Jae Gyeong
have the original CCTV footage?

368
00:26:12.933 --> 00:26:14.433
You said you took care of everything.

369
00:26:14.703 --> 00:26:16.873
Are you blaming your father now?

370
00:26:17.133 --> 00:26:18.593
You were the one who
got angry. asking how long...

371
00:26:18.673 --> 00:26:20.073
I'd rely on others to take over Choiseong!

372
00:26:21.043 --> 00:26:22.643
You're the one who
pushed me into this. Father.

373
00:26:24.273 --> 00:26:26.043
Deep down. you wanted me to
finish the job myself. didn't you?

374
00:26:26.513 --> 00:26:29.053
- So what?
- When Chairman Kang died.

375
00:26:29.683 --> 00:26:31.623
you were the one who was happiest.

376
00:26:35.723 --> 00:26:37.153
I'm just saying I haven't done anything...

377
00:26:37.753 --> 00:26:39.493
to deserve this humiliation.

378
00:26:41.833 --> 00:26:43.483
- Hey. stop them.
- You can't go in.

379
00:26:43.563 --> 00:26:46.063
- Who do you think you are?
- Hey. who are you people?

380
00:26:46.203 --> 00:26:48.023
Jo Taek Sang. we're arresting you...

381
00:26:48.103 --> 00:26:49.503
for trespassing and the
theft of industrial technology.

382
00:26:49.703 --> 00:26:50.923
You have the right to an attorney...

383
00:26:51.003 --> 00:26:52.243
and an opportunity to make a statement.

384
00:26:52.373 --> 00:26:54.043
You also have the right to remain silent.

385
00:26:55.343 --> 00:26:57.043
Regarding the stolen industrial technology.

386
00:26:57.673 --> 00:26:59.503
the Taeha executives
and even you. Chairman.

387
00:26:59.583 --> 00:27:01.783
may also be investigated.

388
00:27:06.683 --> 00:27:08.123
Father.

389
00:27:12.363 --> 00:27:15.393
(Kang Jae Gyeong)

390
00:27:33.683 --> 00:27:34.683
This way.

391
00:27:39.883 --> 00:27:40.883
Brains always win. don't they?

392
00:27:42.553 --> 00:27:44.693
Looks like you'll need to hire
a new secretary. Chairman.

393
00:27:45.423 --> 00:27:48.063
I wonder if you'll find someone as
talented as my Team Leader Hwang.

394
00:27:49.493 --> 00:27:52.283
After all. my Team Leader
Hwang found the phone...

395
00:27:52.363 --> 00:27:54.333
of the security guard you killed.

396
00:27:55.173 --> 00:27:56.903
There was a lot of interesting stuff on it.

397
00:27:57.473 --> 00:28:00.143
I should've killed that jerk too.

398
00:28:03.913 --> 00:28:06.843
Thanks to you. I laughed so
hard I cried for the first time in ages.

399
00:28:08.013 --> 00:28:09.683
You're really something else.

400
00:28:10.253 --> 00:28:13.183
Telling your precious
daughter to kill someone.

401
00:28:14.323 --> 00:28:16.793
You know. I'm almost starting
to feel sorry for you. Eun Se.

402
00:28:18.363 --> 00:28:19.363
By the way.

403
00:28:20.263 --> 00:28:21.563
if it gets out that you killed my father.

404
00:28:22.793 --> 00:28:25.003
in an attempt to take over Choiseong.

405
00:28:26.703 --> 00:28:28.303
do you think Taeha will be able to survive?

406
00:28:31.873 --> 00:28:33.373
I tend to be softhearted.

407
00:28:35.313 --> 00:28:36.643
Give me Taeha Energy.

408
00:28:38.043 --> 00:28:40.283
I was nearly framed for
murdering my own father.

409
00:28:40.683 --> 00:28:43.313
So that's the least I deserve
if you expect me to help you.

410
00:28:45.753 --> 00:28:47.753
As for the acquisition
fee for Taeha Energy.

411
00:28:48.823 --> 00:28:50.593
you'll be the one footing
the bill. won't you. Chairman?

412
00:28:53.863 --> 00:28:56.433
You have a slush fund
stashed away. don't you?

413
00:28:56.763 --> 00:28:57.763
In Singapore.

414
00:29:13.843 --> 00:29:15.553
(Statement of Account)

415
00:29:16.213 --> 00:29:18.923
My Team Leader Hwang found that too.

416
00:29:19.883 --> 00:29:21.653
Even I find him scary sometimes.

417
00:29:25.893 --> 00:29:27.423
This must be a lot for you to process.

418
00:29:29.033 --> 00:29:32.163
This isn't a problem you can solve
just by cutting your daughter loose.

419
00:29:32.833 --> 00:29:34.803
- Watch your mouth.
- Keep your voice down.

420
00:29:35.033 --> 00:29:36.033
Father.

421
00:29:43.773 --> 00:29:45.213
Kang Yong Ho's death...

422
00:29:46.983 --> 00:29:49.113
If you agree to bury it
forever. I'll consider it.

423
00:29:51.923 --> 00:29:53.953
The living must go on living.

424
00:29:55.693 --> 00:29:58.163
I'm not so cruel that I would destroy...

425
00:29:59.493 --> 00:30:01.163
the livelihoods of so many people.

426
00:30:16.743 --> 00:30:19.843
How did you find this out?

427
00:30:20.083 --> 00:30:21.333
You once asked Chairman Kang Yong Ho...

428
00:30:21.413 --> 00:30:23.583
about hiding funds overseas. didn't you?

429
00:30:24.823 --> 00:30:27.343
He called you pathetic
and vulgar for trying...

430
00:30:27.423 --> 00:30:29.723
to copy everything a real chairman does.

431
00:30:30.393 --> 00:30:31.493
He certainly gave you an earful for it.

432
00:30:31.893 --> 00:30:33.463
How do you know that?

433
00:30:33.823 --> 00:30:37.333
"Since we're family now. it's
hard to refuse. I'll show you how."

434
00:30:39.463 --> 00:30:42.733
But in the process. he kept
copies of every single document.

435
00:30:43.433 --> 00:30:44.843
(Taeha Group Chairman Na
Byeong Mo's Slush Fund Records)

436
00:30:44.973 --> 00:30:46.993
Of course. I doubt Chairman
Kang ever imagined...

437
00:30:47.073 --> 00:30:49.813
he'd have to play this card
under these circumstances.

438
00:30:50.043 --> 00:30:54.283
Chairman Kang told you this?
Why? What are you to him?

439
00:30:54.613 --> 00:30:55.613
Indeed.

440
00:30:57.613 --> 00:30:58.823
Who could I be?

441
00:31:01.823 --> 00:31:03.493
Get ready to enter Singapore.

442
00:31:04.153 --> 00:31:05.863
Get it done as soon as possible.

443
00:31:14.733 --> 00:31:18.373
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

444
00:31:22.013 --> 00:31:24.313
Thanks to you. Team Leader
Hwang. I kept my position...

445
00:31:24.743 --> 00:31:26.243
and even got my hands on Taeha Energy.

446
00:31:27.983 --> 00:31:29.713
It's something even my father couldn't do.

447
00:31:30.283 --> 00:31:31.823
I. Kang Jae Gyeong. have done it.

448
00:31:32.323 --> 00:31:34.923
Seriously. what would I do without you?

449
00:31:38.423 --> 00:31:41.933
Should we try to take over all of Taeha?

450
00:31:43.863 --> 00:31:45.033
Says who?

451
00:31:52.073 --> 00:31:55.613
- Where have you been so late?
- Oh. I was just...

452
00:31:56.513 --> 00:31:59.013
- out for a walk.
- Why? That's dangerous.

453
00:32:04.483 --> 00:32:05.953
It'll be over soon.

454
00:32:07.783 --> 00:32:09.293
Kang Jae Gyeong and Taeha.

455
00:32:15.493 --> 00:32:16.993
About your brother-in-law...

456
00:32:21.773 --> 00:32:22.773
No. It's just...

457
00:32:24.473 --> 00:32:25.943
You're going on a business trip tomorrow?

458
00:32:37.553 --> 00:32:38.553
Hey.

459
00:32:42.023 --> 00:32:45.143
You came alone? You've got a lot of nerve.

460
00:32:45.223 --> 00:32:47.543
She said if I get so
much as a scratch on me.

461
00:32:47.623 --> 00:32:48.863
she won't let it slide.

462
00:32:51.563 --> 00:32:54.033
Go ahead if you want to
be on the nine o'clock news.

463
00:32:56.003 --> 00:32:57.003
Gosh. I'm so scared.

464
00:32:57.273 --> 00:32:59.763
You're in economy? You're
going on important business.

465
00:32:59.843 --> 00:33:03.473
You should've spent
a little. I'm in first class.

466
00:33:06.083 --> 00:33:07.913
That jerk. Darn it.

467
00:33:12.253 --> 00:33:14.523
Yes. Chairman Kang. I'm boarding now.

468
00:33:15.353 --> 00:33:17.253
Have you hired the people for the laundry?

469
00:33:17.823 --> 00:33:20.023
The guys who helped you
with Siren Capital Partners.

470
00:33:20.293 --> 00:33:22.293
I've arranged for you to
meet them in Singapore.

471
00:33:24.263 --> 00:33:25.923
What about the paper company to launder...

472
00:33:26.003 --> 00:33:27.763
Na Byeong Mo's money and act as a buffer?

473
00:33:28.003 --> 00:33:30.633
I know an expert for that. so don't worry.

474
00:33:30.933 --> 00:33:31.943
Worry?

475
00:33:32.473 --> 00:33:34.603
- Good luck. Team Leader Hwang.
- What?

476
00:33:36.213 --> 00:33:37.213
You should be more careful.

477
00:33:39.643 --> 00:33:40.643
Thank you.

478
00:33:46.683 --> 00:33:49.993
Gosh. why is she dressed so flashily?

479
00:33:53.323 --> 00:33:54.793
Everyone's staring. Darn it.

480
00:33:56.733 --> 00:33:58.233
(Report On Taeha Energy's
Business and Operations)

481
00:34:06.473 --> 00:34:08.123
Let's finalize the M&A
plan for Taeha Energy...

482
00:34:08.203 --> 00:34:11.443
- before Team Leader Hwang is back.
- Yes. ma'am.

483
00:34:13.843 --> 00:34:14.843
And him?

484
00:34:16.213 --> 00:34:17.483
What's he been up to lately?

485
00:34:35.803 --> 00:34:38.703
I kept asking you to go. but you
always said you were too busy.

486
00:34:39.343 --> 00:34:40.403
Look at you. playing golf.

487
00:34:42.513 --> 00:34:45.213
I haven't played in a
while. I'm a bit rusty.

488
00:34:46.583 --> 00:34:47.913
And you've been busy.

489
00:34:50.413 --> 00:34:52.053
You seem different.

490
00:34:52.853 --> 00:34:53.853
Your whole vibe.

491
00:34:55.753 --> 00:34:56.753
I went through something huge.

492
00:34:57.853 --> 00:34:59.293
Anyone would change after that.

493
00:35:10.733 --> 00:35:11.743
What about the car?

494
00:35:13.073 --> 00:35:14.073
Do you like it?

495
00:35:37.363 --> 00:35:39.333
(Recovery From Hypoxic Brain
Injury. a Study on Treatment Strategies)

496
00:35:51.543 --> 00:35:54.883
Are you doing volunteer
work somewhere out of guilt?

497
00:35:55.153 --> 00:35:58.583
Or are you trying to
resurrect our cremated father?

498
00:36:14.263 --> 00:36:16.193
What would everyone
say if a doctor like me...

499
00:36:16.273 --> 00:36:18.133
suddenly started working for the company?

500
00:36:19.043 --> 00:36:21.203
You want me to hear I only
got the job because of my wife?

501
00:36:21.773 --> 00:36:24.293
I don't want to be your parrot
whether it's at Chemical or C&T.

502
00:36:24.373 --> 00:36:26.843
I'm thinking of a Medical
Division focused on neurology.

503
00:36:27.943 --> 00:36:31.013
I got interested in coma
cases while treating Father.

504
00:36:36.693 --> 00:36:37.843
You quit the hospital...

505
00:36:37.923 --> 00:36:40.523
but took syringes and
coma treatments with you.

506
00:36:42.233 --> 00:36:43.393
I was wondering...

507
00:36:44.793 --> 00:36:46.003
what you were up to.

508
00:36:46.963 --> 00:36:47.963
Jae Gyeong.

509
00:36:50.133 --> 00:36:51.133
Are you scared?

510
00:36:52.473 --> 00:36:53.973
That I might leave you too?

511
00:36:56.473 --> 00:36:57.473
Leave?

512
00:36:58.413 --> 00:36:59.643
I abandoned them.

513
00:37:00.513 --> 00:37:02.773
That ill-fated connection.
clinging on because of blood ties...

514
00:37:02.853 --> 00:37:04.283
I'm the one who ended it.

515
00:37:05.323 --> 00:37:07.423
The only family I need is you and Il Jun.

516
00:37:11.523 --> 00:37:14.723
I'll tell them to move forward
with the Medical Division.

517
00:37:17.163 --> 00:37:18.663
I'm the chairwoman of Choiseong.

518
00:37:19.903 --> 00:37:21.603
You have no reason to feel inferior.

519
00:37:31.143 --> 00:37:32.183
Take me to the office.

520
00:37:32.383 --> 00:37:33.443
Yes. ma'am.

521
00:37:34.413 --> 00:37:36.013
The Task Force has a lot on its plate.

522
00:37:36.713 --> 00:37:37.713
You're going home. right?

523
00:37:38.413 --> 00:37:39.423
Yes.

524
00:38:18.863 --> 00:38:21.723
Sir. we absolutely cannot lose that car.

525
00:38:50.823 --> 00:38:52.523
Mother?

526
00:38:58.163 --> 00:39:00.633
Wait. please. Just hear me out first.

527
00:39:05.033 --> 00:39:06.043
Mother!

528
00:39:14.243 --> 00:39:15.613
What are you doing here?

529
00:39:40.043 --> 00:39:41.043
This is what you've been doing...

530
00:39:43.373 --> 00:39:45.143
behind my back?

531
00:39:46.813 --> 00:39:47.813
I'm sorry.

532
00:39:48.583 --> 00:39:49.583
I was just afraid...

533
00:39:50.453 --> 00:39:54.223
that if something happened to
Father again. it would be too painful.

534
00:39:54.853 --> 00:39:56.523
I didn't have the courage.

535
00:39:57.293 --> 00:39:58.993
and I was too scared to tell you.

536
00:39:59.893 --> 00:40:00.963
I have no excuse.

537
00:40:08.673 --> 00:40:09.903
Thank you. Jae Seong.

538
00:40:14.303 --> 00:40:15.313
Thank you.

539
00:40:16.073 --> 00:40:17.543
For saving your father.

540
00:40:20.713 --> 00:40:23.083
For letting me see him again.

541
00:40:27.923 --> 00:40:29.423
Thank you so much. Jae Seong.

542
00:40:30.423 --> 00:40:31.423
I'll make sure...

543
00:40:32.623 --> 00:40:34.723
Father wakes up.

544
00:40:35.693 --> 00:40:36.733
Mother.

545
00:40:46.373 --> 00:40:49.013
Are they really giving the
slush fund to Kang Jae Gyeong?

546
00:40:49.613 --> 00:40:50.613
Of course not.

547
00:40:52.213 --> 00:40:53.713
This is Na Byeong Mo's slush fund file.

548
00:40:54.543 --> 00:40:56.033
It has everything. The
Singapore account information.

549
00:40:56.113 --> 00:40:57.583
even the accounts under other names.

550
00:40:58.783 --> 00:41:01.823
Hwang Jun Hyeon gave this to
me and said to turn it in to the police.

551
00:41:02.723 --> 00:41:06.323
Then why did those two take Na
Eun Se all the way to Singapore?

552
00:41:06.693 --> 00:41:07.993
Bang Geul posed a question.

553
00:41:08.993 --> 00:41:09.993
She asked...

554
00:41:10.833 --> 00:41:12.453
how strong do you think the bond is...

555
00:41:12.533 --> 00:41:14.333
between a father and daughter
who have even killed someone?

556
00:41:14.833 --> 00:41:17.503
His daughter probably isn't
one of Na Byeong Mo's options.

557
00:41:18.233 --> 00:41:20.143
He's just worried about
tarnishing the group's image.

558
00:41:20.443 --> 00:41:21.443
Bingo.

559
00:41:22.043 --> 00:41:23.673
She said that's what
they were going to exploit.

560
00:41:23.873 --> 00:41:26.143
What are you two doing? Get out here.

561
00:41:26.613 --> 00:41:28.413
- We're coming.
- Yes.

562
00:41:28.983 --> 00:41:31.013
- Yes.
- Goodness.

563
00:41:34.553 --> 00:41:37.393
We'll keep you safe
until your son gets back.

564
00:41:37.623 --> 00:41:40.963
Just think of us as two new sons.
You can rely on us. can't you?

565
00:41:42.333 --> 00:41:43.713
I cooked a free-range chicken.

566
00:41:43.793 --> 00:41:46.363
- Sit down.
- Oh. really?

567
00:41:47.003 --> 00:41:48.053
But...

568
00:41:48.133 --> 00:41:51.233
I knew I was smelling something delicious.

569
00:41:52.773 --> 00:41:55.173
We came here to look after you. though.

570
00:41:55.373 --> 00:41:58.073
I heard you've been a
big help to my Jun Hyeon.

571
00:41:58.713 --> 00:42:00.383
The young woman next door told me...

572
00:42:00.643 --> 00:42:02.753
- that you're my boy's best friend.
- Yes.

573
00:42:03.113 --> 00:42:04.103
You drink. right?

574
00:42:04.183 --> 00:42:06.043
You even brought out liquor. Thank you.

575
00:42:06.123 --> 00:42:07.873
You just sit tight. I'll get
it ready and bring it out.

576
00:42:07.953 --> 00:42:08.953
Wonderful.

577
00:42:09.353 --> 00:42:10.443
- I'll bring it over.
- It looks like...

578
00:42:10.523 --> 00:42:12.593
we're the ones being treated.

579
00:42:15.393 --> 00:42:17.993
- Crying again?
- I'm going through menopause.

580
00:42:18.733 --> 00:42:20.883
Jun Hyeon. that punk. I
can't wait for him to get back.

581
00:42:20.963 --> 00:42:23.823
I'm really going to treat
him well from now on.

582
00:42:23.903 --> 00:42:25.803
Gosh. It's okay.

583
00:42:26.343 --> 00:42:27.403
Take a seat.

584
00:42:28.173 --> 00:42:32.113
(Singapore)

585
00:42:32.543 --> 00:42:34.643
Write down Chairman Na's
Singapore account here.

586
00:42:35.883 --> 00:42:38.943
Take seven percent. send the
rest to this foundation account.

587
00:42:39.023 --> 00:42:40.153
(International Wire Transfer Request)

588
00:42:44.823 --> 00:42:48.263
A 7-percent commission?
So they take 35 million dollars.

589
00:42:48.993 --> 00:42:52.603
and Kang Jae Gyeong just gets to
gobble up over 450 million dollars.

590
00:42:55.633 --> 00:42:56.733
Just sign it.

591
00:42:59.643 --> 00:43:00.643
JH?

592
00:43:01.643 --> 00:43:03.173
JH. as in Hwang Jun Hyeon?

593
00:43:04.343 --> 00:43:06.983
For a company that you'll shut
down after laundering the money.

594
00:43:07.583 --> 00:43:08.913
the name's a bit on the
nose. don't you think?

595
00:43:09.013 --> 00:43:11.613
An expert put a lot of thought
and effort into that name.

596
00:43:11.913 --> 00:43:15.023
Who knows? It might become a
truly prestigious soccer foundation.

597
00:43:15.323 --> 00:43:16.753
Go on. order some champagne.

598
00:43:17.823 --> 00:43:19.293
We've got a lot of time
to kill before our flight.

599
00:43:20.163 --> 00:43:21.493
Let me walk you out.

600
00:43:23.233 --> 00:43:24.393
Excuse me.

601
00:43:29.403 --> 00:43:30.403
You guys...

602
00:43:31.373 --> 00:43:33.243
better make this flight worthwhile.

603
00:43:40.713 --> 00:43:41.743
(Kang Bang Geul: Let's Begin. Jae Seong.)

604
00:43:41.843 --> 00:43:42.853
Let's begin. Jae Seong.

605
00:43:46.883 --> 00:43:48.553
(President Jeong. Hayoung Daily)

606
00:43:53.023 --> 00:43:54.793
It's me. Kang Jae Seong.

607
00:44:15.483 --> 00:44:16.553
Are you sure about this?

608
00:44:17.283 --> 00:44:18.943
- You'd do this to me?
- Don't be so cocky...

609
00:44:19.023 --> 00:44:20.123
just because you've got Kang Jae Gyeon.

610
00:44:20.983 --> 00:44:22.993
There are plenty of guys like
you for her to use and toss aside.

611
00:44:24.353 --> 00:44:25.823
Who says I'm relying on Kang Jae Gyeong?

612
00:44:37.173 --> 00:44:39.143
So the Daesan Hydrogen Complex
incident wasn't a coincidence.

613
00:44:39.803 --> 00:44:41.043
You were pretending to be
on Kang Jae Gyeong's sie.

614
00:44:42.143 --> 00:44:44.163
You were working with
Kang Bang Geul all along?

615
00:44:44.243 --> 00:44:45.983
You've been fooling all of us?

616
00:44:50.753 --> 00:44:52.883
I'm glad you caught on.
It makes things easier.

617
00:44:56.693 --> 00:44:57.823
I doubt he'll answer.

618
00:44:58.653 --> 00:45:00.423
Chairman Na must be
going through hell right now.

619
00:45:02.733 --> 00:45:05.253
{\an8}This is breaking news. The
culprit who killed Kang Yong Ho.

620
00:45:05.333 --> 00:45:06.863
{\an8}the former chairman of Choiseong Group.

621
00:45:07.163 --> 00:45:09.053
{\an8}is believed to be the
deceased's daughter-in-law.

622
00:45:09.133 --> 00:45:10.573
{\an8}Ms. Na. which comes as a great shock.

623
00:45:10.903 --> 00:45:13.703
{\an8}With the release of footage
that clearly captures her face.

624
00:45:14.103 --> 00:45:16.363
{\an8}the controversy surrounding the death...

625
00:45:16.443 --> 00:45:18.613
of the late Chairman Kang
Yong Ho is expected to grow.

626
00:45:20.043 --> 00:45:22.453
If you don't want to get arrested
by the police like Secretary Jo.

627
00:45:23.313 --> 00:45:24.913
it's every man for himself from now on.

628
00:45:31.793 --> 00:45:33.263
So you took the slush fund too?

629
00:45:35.863 --> 00:45:37.433
Did you bring me here
from the start just for this?

630
00:45:37.863 --> 00:45:39.433
To get me trapped and
arrested in a foreign country?

631
00:45:39.803 --> 00:45:41.063
Hwang Jun Hyeon. you jerk.

632
00:45:43.803 --> 00:45:45.703
This isn't the time for
you to feel wronged.

633
00:45:45.943 --> 00:45:47.863
You should be saying. "I'm not even
human. I've committed a deadly sin."

634
00:45:47.943 --> 00:45:50.213
You should be on your knees
begging Kang Bang Geul for forgiveness.

635
00:45:52.613 --> 00:45:54.243
He was just some old
geezer who was already dead.

636
00:45:54.713 --> 00:45:55.733
Do you have any idea what you've done...

637
00:45:55.813 --> 00:45:56.853
just to find the "real culprit"?

638
00:46:01.553 --> 00:46:03.253
Do you really think my father
will let you get away with this?

639
00:46:06.593 --> 00:46:08.223
It seems you still
have faith in your father.

640
00:46:09.933 --> 00:46:13.363
Do you think Chairman Na will
save you? Or will he save Taeha?

641
00:46:18.703 --> 00:46:19.703
(President Jeon Jin Hwan. Taeha Energy)

642
00:46:22.913 --> 00:46:24.513
(President Shin Yong Ha. Taeha Chemical)

643
00:46:26.843 --> 00:46:28.283
(Eldest Son. Taeha Construction)

644
00:46:33.353 --> 00:46:34.883
(International Call)

645
00:46:39.193 --> 00:46:40.193
Father.

646
00:46:40.423 --> 00:46:42.833
Eun Se. are you all right?

647
00:46:43.433 --> 00:46:45.633
("It is Believed to Be
Daughter-In-Law. Ms. Na")

648
00:46:46.533 --> 00:46:47.953
There's no way Team Leader Hwang...

649
00:46:48.033 --> 00:46:49.703
would release the
footage without my consent.

650
00:46:51.573 --> 00:46:53.273
What in the world is going on?

651
00:46:54.203 --> 00:46:55.443
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

652
00:46:56.313 --> 00:46:57.313
Chairwoman.

653
00:47:21.803 --> 00:47:25.203
(The 3rd Chairwoman of Choiseong Group)

654
00:47:26.373 --> 00:47:28.073
That despicable monster.

655
00:47:30.913 --> 00:47:33.083
Eun Se is no longer my daughter.

656
00:47:34.043 --> 00:47:36.773
I will drag her back myself.
expose all her crimes.

657
00:47:36.853 --> 00:47:38.783
and make sure she pays
for them. Chairwoman Kang.

658
00:47:40.353 --> 00:47:42.493
You must have suffered so much.

659
00:47:42.953 --> 00:47:45.153
We were old friends long
before we became in-laws.

660
00:47:45.963 --> 00:47:48.323
I don't know how I could
ever ask for his forgiveness.

661
00:47:49.093 --> 00:47:50.893
Failing to control my own
daughter after her marriage...

662
00:47:51.163 --> 00:47:53.223
and knowing nothing
while things got this bad.

663
00:47:53.303 --> 00:47:55.363
It is my sin. But...

664
00:47:56.333 --> 00:47:57.873
allow me to apologize on her behalf.

665
00:48:10.113 --> 00:48:11.453
There are too many people watching.

666
00:48:12.353 --> 00:48:13.923
Let's go somewhere else to talk.

667
00:48:16.823 --> 00:48:17.853
Chairman Na Byeong Mo.

668
00:48:20.123 --> 00:48:22.963
Ms. Na Eun Se flew to Singapore yesterday.

669
00:48:23.993 --> 00:48:26.023
I have no intention of covering
up my daughter's crimes.

670
00:48:26.103 --> 00:48:27.703
I will cooperate fully.

671
00:48:28.203 --> 00:48:31.193
- As soon as she's back in Korea...
- You didn't help her flee...

672
00:48:31.273 --> 00:48:32.943
to launder your slush fund too?

673
00:48:33.743 --> 00:48:34.743
What?

674
00:48:37.313 --> 00:48:40.713
Where's the Anti-Corruption and
Economic Crime Investigation Unit?

675
00:48:41.183 --> 00:48:42.343
It's this way. sir.

676
00:48:43.183 --> 00:48:44.183
Thank you.

677
00:48:44.283 --> 00:48:45.583
(The People's Police)

678
00:48:47.983 --> 00:48:50.653
(Data On Taeha Group Chairman
Na Byeong Mo's Slush Fund)

679
00:48:51.653 --> 00:48:53.593
Special delivery. hot off the press.

680
00:48:53.693 --> 00:48:55.563
(Anti-Corruption and Economic
Crime Investigation Unit)

681
00:48:55.863 --> 00:48:57.913
Do you have any idea how
many people have tried...

682
00:48:57.993 --> 00:48:59.833
to take me down with bogus tips like that?

683
00:49:00.233 --> 00:49:02.263
Well then. you know Ham Du Ho. don't you?

684
00:49:03.233 --> 00:49:04.393
He was a security guard...

685
00:49:04.473 --> 00:49:06.503
at Hangang University
Hospital. He died recently.

686
00:49:08.973 --> 00:49:11.993
To be precise. it was a homicide.
We've secured evidence...

687
00:49:12.073 --> 00:49:14.113
suggesting that you. Chairman
Na. ordered the murder.

688
00:49:14.383 --> 00:49:15.503
What nonsense?

689
00:49:15.583 --> 00:49:17.653
I heard that guy contacted you too.

690
00:49:18.983 --> 00:49:21.553
You're saying there's another
video on the security guard's phone?

691
00:49:21.853 --> 00:49:24.793
He said he'd tell you what really
happened that day for a hefty price.

692
00:49:25.053 --> 00:49:27.493
He shouldn't have pushed his luck.

693
00:49:27.993 --> 00:49:29.063
Isn't that right?

694
00:49:30.793 --> 00:49:33.233
The security guard's
glasses had a built-in camera.

695
00:49:33.503 --> 00:49:34.733
Secretary Jo bribing him...

696
00:49:35.003 --> 00:49:36.933
and even him stealing the
hospital's CCTV footage.

697
00:49:37.403 --> 00:49:38.573
It's all recorded.

698
00:49:39.033 --> 00:49:41.243
Let's show the world
just what kind of man...

699
00:49:41.573 --> 00:49:44.643
Na Byeong Mo is. Sang Jae.

700
00:49:46.613 --> 00:49:48.343
That voice isn't mine.

701
00:49:49.083 --> 00:49:50.133
Someone must have fabricated it.

702
00:49:50.213 --> 00:49:51.753
just like Chairman Kang
Jae Gyeong's recording.

703
00:49:52.183 --> 00:49:54.903
My secretary. That jerk killed
him on his own out of loyalty...

704
00:49:54.983 --> 00:49:56.243
and framed me for it.

705
00:49:56.323 --> 00:49:59.493
We'll find that out when we question
you and your secretary together.

706
00:49:59.763 --> 00:50:01.143
We've put out an Interpol notice.

707
00:50:01.223 --> 00:50:03.483
so you'll be seeing your
daughter soon enough.

708
00:50:03.563 --> 00:50:06.603
I didn't know anything. I.
Na Byeong Mo. am innocent.

709
00:50:06.903 --> 00:50:08.803
I said get your hands off me!

710
00:50:09.633 --> 00:50:10.633
How dare you.

711
00:50:16.443 --> 00:50:19.733
Police have launched a
surprise raid on Taeha Group.

712
00:50:19.813 --> 00:50:21.663
The group allegedly failed
to pay for the acquisition...

713
00:50:21.743 --> 00:50:23.433
of Choiseong C&T's hydrogen business...

714
00:50:23.513 --> 00:50:24.873
and stole its core technology.

715
00:50:24.953 --> 00:50:27.843
Authorities are now tracking a
300 million dollar corporate loan...

716
00:50:27.923 --> 00:50:30.273
that Taeha took out.
ostensibly for the acquisition.

717
00:50:30.353 --> 00:50:32.273
It was also announced that
they will cooperate closely...

718
00:50:32.353 --> 00:50:33.943
with authorities in Singapore.

719
00:50:34.023 --> 00:50:35.713
where Chairman Na Byeong Mo is believed...

720
00:50:35.793 --> 00:50:37.163
to have hidden his slush fund.

721
00:50:40.203 --> 00:50:42.153
Meanwhile. Na Eun Se. who
was named as the suspect...

722
00:50:42.233 --> 00:50:44.493
in the murder of the late
Choiseong Chairman Kang Yong Ho.

723
00:50:44.573 --> 00:50:47.043
is currently missing.

724
00:50:47.203 --> 00:50:50.373
Her father. Chairman Na Byeong
Mo. who is under police investigation.

725
00:50:50.543 --> 00:50:53.663
has reportedly stated that
his daughter. Na Eun Se.

726
00:50:53.743 --> 00:50:56.083
acted alone in committing the crime.

727
00:50:56.253 --> 00:50:58.353
Eun Se is no longer my daughter.

728
00:50:58.813 --> 00:51:01.543
I will drag her back myself.
expose all her crimes.

729
00:51:01.623 --> 00:51:03.393
and make sure she pays
for them. Chairwoman Kang.

730
00:51:06.163 --> 00:51:07.163
Eun Se.

731
00:51:07.563 --> 00:51:10.163
- Are you all right?
- We really got played.

732
00:51:10.493 --> 00:51:13.303
- That jerk Hwang Jun Hyeon...
- Don't come back to Korea.

733
00:51:15.303 --> 00:51:19.373
- What?
- Go to Florida. hide out at villa.

734
00:51:20.603 --> 00:51:22.193
- Father.
- That's the best way...

735
00:51:22.273 --> 00:51:24.113
to sort things out here.

736
00:51:24.413 --> 00:51:26.463
There's no conclusive
evidence and no suspect.

737
00:51:26.543 --> 00:51:28.703
The investigation? It'll
drag on and go nowhere.

738
00:51:28.783 --> 00:51:32.853
Just do as I say until then. It's
the only way we both survive.

739
00:51:33.323 --> 00:51:34.583
Do you understand your father?

740
00:51:35.753 --> 00:51:36.753
Eun Se.

741
00:51:37.493 --> 00:51:39.623
Eun Se. Na Eun Se!

742
00:51:40.763 --> 00:51:43.033
He sounds so desperate to
abandon his own daughter.

743
00:51:43.693 --> 00:51:44.693
Shut it.

744
00:51:44.963 --> 00:51:45.963
All right. then.

745
00:51:46.433 --> 00:51:48.053
Go ahead and play the tragic heroine.

746
00:51:48.133 --> 00:51:50.173
taking all the blame and
sacrificing for your father.

747
00:51:50.633 --> 00:51:51.833
I said. shut it!

748
00:52:11.493 --> 00:52:14.463
Do I die. or do I kill my father?

749
00:52:15.293 --> 00:52:17.063
Na Eun Se has a lot to think about.

750
00:52:17.263 --> 00:52:18.913
Now that she's seen her father abandon her.

751
00:52:18.993 --> 00:52:21.163
she's probably figuring out
the best way to destroy him.

752
00:52:31.313 --> 00:52:32.313
Yes. Chairwoman.

753
00:52:32.573 --> 00:52:34.043
Why have you been so hard to reach?

754
00:52:34.813 --> 00:52:36.453
I just arrived.

755
00:52:37.083 --> 00:52:38.483
I'll head straight back to the office.

756
00:52:39.083 --> 00:52:40.923
I have so much to tell you.

757
00:52:41.283 --> 00:52:42.793
All right. Team Leader Hwang.

758
00:52:44.323 --> 00:52:47.863
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

759
00:52:47.993 --> 00:52:50.833
Can I get you anything?
You haven't had dinner yet.

760
00:52:51.163 --> 00:52:52.233
I'm not hungry.

761
00:52:53.403 --> 00:52:54.763
You can go home now. Secretary Yeo.

762
00:52:55.363 --> 00:52:57.173
And tell the Task Force
they're disbanded as of today.

763
00:53:09.613 --> 00:53:11.083
Has Kang Jae Seong gone home yet?

764
00:53:33.273 --> 00:53:35.273
(Available)

765
00:53:35.543 --> 00:53:36.813
Call me if anything happens.

766
00:53:37.273 --> 00:53:38.943
Don't try to be a hero all by yourself.

767
00:53:39.173 --> 00:53:40.943
Stop nagging and just go.

768
00:53:41.183 --> 00:53:44.713
Call me. no matter
how late it is. All right?

769
00:53:47.683 --> 00:53:49.353
Please drive safely.

770
00:53:51.123 --> 00:53:52.193
You said okay.

771
00:55:03.693 --> 00:55:06.033
Was there not enough evidence?

772
00:55:06.533 --> 00:55:08.933
Is their legal team just that good?

773
00:55:09.403 --> 00:55:11.603
I didn't expect him to get out so soon.

774
00:55:12.103 --> 00:55:14.773
I'm the chairman of a
major corporation. after all.

775
00:55:15.303 --> 00:55:16.713
I was surprised too.

776
00:55:17.073 --> 00:55:19.813
This is the first time I've
been blindsided this badly.

777
00:55:26.723 --> 00:55:28.923
Just to save his own skin.

778
00:55:29.283 --> 00:55:31.673
he backstabs his daughter.

779
00:55:31.753 --> 00:55:33.723
- What a load of nonsense.
- What?

780
00:55:36.123 --> 00:55:38.763
You can't wash away the
stink of who you are. can you?

781
00:55:40.603 --> 00:55:44.603
No matter what expensive clothes
you wear or what fancy title you have.

782
00:55:45.833 --> 00:55:49.243
- your rotten nature never changes.
- You son of a witch.

783
00:55:54.013 --> 00:55:55.143
That look in your eyes.

784
00:55:56.413 --> 00:55:58.513
And the way you run your
mouth without a shred of fear...

785
00:55:59.313 --> 00:56:01.123
You're just like him.

786
00:56:02.723 --> 00:56:04.223
Don't you recognize me?

787
00:56:05.953 --> 00:56:06.963
It's me.

788
00:56:08.423 --> 00:56:10.433
Kang Yong Ho. The man you killed.

789
00:56:17.103 --> 00:56:20.673
You knew you couldn't beat me
unless you killed me. didn't you?

790
00:56:21.873 --> 00:56:24.563
Aren't you ashamed for
causing this whole mess...

791
00:56:24.643 --> 00:56:27.113
just so you could dance on my
grave and congratulate yourself?

792
00:56:29.953 --> 00:56:32.103
It's all temporary. It's over when you die.

793
00:56:32.183 --> 00:56:33.623
so what more could you want?

794
00:56:33.953 --> 00:56:36.553
You jerk! Hey!

795
00:56:37.853 --> 00:56:39.763
You think I can't see right through you?

796
00:56:40.993 --> 00:56:42.413
Trying to take over Choiseong...

797
00:56:42.493 --> 00:56:44.733
with your petty revenge
and childish obsession.

798
00:56:44.893 --> 00:56:46.233
I'm impressed!

799
00:56:46.433 --> 00:56:50.273
I admire that kind of nerve!

800
00:56:51.003 --> 00:56:52.033
But...

801
00:56:53.903 --> 00:56:55.103
you're not on my side.

802
00:57:05.913 --> 00:57:07.253
Give Kang Yong Ho...

803
00:57:08.553 --> 00:57:09.753
my regards.

804
00:57:45.323 --> 00:57:46.763
Why is he calling instead of coming?

805
00:57:55.903 --> 00:57:58.333
(Father)

806
00:58:06.513 --> 00:58:07.563
(Missed Call: Father)

807
00:58:07.643 --> 00:58:08.743
(Father)

808
00:58:20.293 --> 00:58:21.393
(Father)

809
00:58:21.493 --> 00:58:23.993
You had your time ruling the world.
That should have been enough.

810
00:58:24.893 --> 00:58:26.933
How long are you going to stand in my way?

811
00:58:27.433 --> 00:58:29.203
What are you still clinging to?

812
00:58:29.533 --> 00:58:32.633
Should I put an end to it for you?

813
00:59:05.973 --> 00:59:12.543
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

814
00:59:30.133 --> 00:59:31.163
Father?

815
00:59:48.243 --> 00:59:50.153
You should be happy.

816
00:59:51.253 --> 00:59:53.883
Your dead father has
come back from the grave.

817
01:00:08.363 --> 01:00:11.333
(Reborn Rookie)
